    {
        "content": "<p>When I came out of tutorials I basically just know <code>rfl</code>, <code>rw</code>, <code>apply</code>, <code>repeat</code>, <code>induction</code>, <code>cases</code>, <code>assumption</code> and <code>exact</code></p>",
